<main class="mx-auto max-w-lg px-4 py-16" dir="rtl"><h1 class="text-3xl font-black">تفعيل حسابك</h1><p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">اختر كلمة مرور قوية لإكمال الدعوة. الدور محدد مسبقًا ولا يمكن تغييره هنا.</p><% if @errors.present? %><div class="mt-5 rounded-xl bg-red-50 p-4 text-red-800" role="alert"><%= @errors.join("، ") %></div><% end %><%= form_with url: invitation_path(token: @token), method: :patch, class: "mt-7 space-y-5" do |form| %><div><%= form.label :password, "كلمة المرور", class: "block font-bold" %><%= form.password_field :password, required: true, minlength: 6, autocomplete: "new-password", class: "mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border p-3" %></div><div><%= form.label :password_confirmation, "تأكيد كلمة المرور", class: "block font-bold" %><%= form.password_field :password_confirmation, required: true, autocomplete: "new-password", class: "mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border p-3" %></div><%= form.submit "تفعيل الحساب", class: "w-full rounded-xl bg-pharmacy-700 p-3 font-bold text-white" %><% end %></main>
